---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Pottery Bowl Painting Session"
  description="Paint beautiful ceramic bowls to add to your collection in Centerville, TN. Functional art you create yourself!"
  price="$12-18"
  duration="1-2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="bowl painting, ceramic bowls, pottery bowls, decorative bowls, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Pottery Bowl Painting Session - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>Create beautiful, functional ceramic bowls that are both decorative and practical. Paint your own unique design on quality pottery bowls at Made @ The Local and take home pieces you'll treasure.</p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>Select from our collection of beautifully shaped ceramic bowls in various sizes and styles. Paint them with professional-grade ceramic paints, creating designs that match your home décor or personal style. Whether you want geometric patterns, floral designs, abstract art, or something uniquely personal, the creative direction is entirely yours. Our instructors provide technique guidance but won't limit your vision. After painting, we professionally glaze and kiln-fire your bowls so they're food-safe, dishwasher-safe, and built to last. You'll leave with functional works of art perfect for serving, storing, or displaying.</p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>High-quality ceramic bowl(s)</li>
      <li>Professional ceramic paints and colors</li>
      <li>Quality brushes and painting supplies</li>
      <li>Expert guidance on design and technique</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Food-safe and dishwasher-safe finished bowls</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Creating functional home décor</li>
      <li>Custom gifts for any occasion</li>
      <li>Serving bowls for entertaining</li>
      <li>Decorative pieces for display</li>
      <li>Organizing and storage with style</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Select your bowl(s) and design idea (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Paint your beautiful design (45-60 minutes)</li>
      <li>Final touches and color blending (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Professional glazing and kiln-firing</li>
      <li>Pick up finished bowls in 2 weeks</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $12-18 per bowl<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 1-2 hours<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Paint your ceramic bowls!</strong> Call (931) XXX-XXXX or email info@thelocalplace.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Painted bowls for my kitchen! They're so pretty and functional. Use them every day for serving and storage!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Patricia L.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Made four matching bowls as a wedding gift. The couple uses them to serve food at dinner parties. Such a unique gift!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Susan M.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"My decorated bowls are conversation starters! Everyone asks where I got them when they're really mine. Love this!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Amanda V.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint Your Own Pottery Session</h3>
        <p>Choose from pre-made pottery pieces and paint them your way.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/paint-your-own-pottery-session" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Personalized Plate Painting</h3>
        <p>Create custom painted dinnerware pieces.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/personalized-plate-painting" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Ceramic Painting Workshop</h3>
        <p>Learn professional ceramic painting techniques in our structured workshop.</p>
        <a href="/pottery-store/ceramic-painting-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
